html.basic:
// Removes 'readonly' attributes from a type's properties
type CreateMutable<Type> = {
  -readonly [Property in keyof Type]: Type[Property];
};


type LockedAccount = {
  readonly id: string;
  readonly name: string;
};


type UnlockedAccount = CreateMutable<LockedAccount>;
